'''Toyaka''' (1997-2025) was a Korean Tabby Cat who lived a loving life on Incheon and mother of eight offspring. 

== Biography ==
Toyaka was born in Residence, she was born in a bathtub, his owner is Ntuthuko Makeba, an lawyer (b. 1967) and he has another pets, an Pointer named Hardy and a rabbit named Ya,

== Footnotes ==

* Life played on August 5, 2025
* Obtained "Aristocat" Ribbon
